Description:
	Yeoman generator to create a wordpress project

    This generator will download Wordpress and a starter theme.
    Most of the default values for the informations asked when
    using this generator are stored in a config file you can edit.
    See https://github.com/romainberger/yeoman-wordpress#configuration
    for more informations

Example:
	yeoman init yeoman-wordpress

	This will create (simplified):

		.
		|-- .gitattributes
		|-- .gitignore
		|-- Gruntfile.js
		|-- app
		|	// wordpress files
		|	...
		|-- package.json